</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Hire_for_potential_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1684339307" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Hire_for_potential_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.jpg?v=1684339307 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Hire_for_potential_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.jpg?v=1684339307 320w" width="5400" height="3024" alt="Hire for potential - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Hire for potential - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-uojGG kTBJzQ pf-44_"/><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-45_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-47_">Organisations should focus on potential, not just past experience, when hiring for leadership roles. This is particularly important for geographically dispersed teams, as leaders must navigate new territories and sustain long-term success. Traits such as adaptability, learning agility, and a growth mindset are indicators of long-term success.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-dFtzxp icSyEj pf-48_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-50_">Focus on key competencies and traits
</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Focus_on_key_competencies_and_traits_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.png?v=1684340472" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Focus_on_key_competencies_and_traits_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.png?v=1684340472 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Focus_on_key_competencies_and_traits_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.png?v=1684340472 320w" width="1382" height="922" alt="Focus on key competencies and traits - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Focus on key competencies and traits - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-uojGG kTBJzQ pf-51_"/><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-52_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-54_">Organisations should identify the key competencies and traits required for leadership roles. In the tech industry, staying up-to-date with the latest trends and innovations is crucial. Empathy, caring for others, and compliance standards are essential in health and social care. Organisations can ensure new leaders fit the organisational culture and contribute to the organisation.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-dFtzxp icSyEj pf-55_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-57_">Utilise objective assessments and data
</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Utilise_objective_assessments_and_data_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.png?v=1684340603" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Utilise_objective_assessments_and_data_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.png?v=1684340603 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Utilise_objective_assessments_and_data_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.png?v=1684340603 320w" width="3242" height="2161" alt="Utilise objective assessments and data - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Utilise objective assessments and data - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-uojGG kTBJzQ pf-58_"/><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-59_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-61_">Objective assessments can be utilised to minimise bias when assessing leadership potential. For the tech industry, cognitive ability and problem-solving capabilities are often used. In health and social care, evaluating interpersonal skills, leadership styles, and compliance standards can ensure the right person is hired.
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-dFtzxp icSyEj pf-62_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-64_">Provide ongoing development and support
